      <p>
        Hi 👋 I'm <strong>Jacques Dumora</strong>, a Machine Learning Engineer based in Paris, France.
        Passionate about cutting-edge technologies and data science, I specialize in crafting innovative
        and efficient solutions to tackle both today's challenges and those of the future.
      </p>
      <h2>What I do</h2>
      <p>
        Whether it's <strong>machine learning</strong>, <strong>data modeling</strong>, <strong>software engineering</strong> or <strong>AI-driven systems</strong>, my goal is to merge technical excellence with elegant design to provide real value.
      </p>
      <h2>On this blog</h2>
      <p>
        I write about building things from scratch to truly understand them — like
        <a href="/blog/de-zero-a-chatgpt-part-1">a deep learning framework in pure Numpy</a>,
        from the humble perceptron all the way to the Transformer architecture.
      </p>
      <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
      <p>
        Feel free to explore some of my coding endeavors on <a href="https://github.com/Jacqkues">GitHub</a>, follow me on <a href="https://x.com/_jacqD">Twitter/X</a>, or <a href="/contact">reach out directly</a>.
      </p>
